    {
      "id": "a7320b3b-3a74-4fe9-8150-8649866db8fa",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "The study focuses on comparing performance and efficiency of different ensemble classifiers for the aforementioned tasks. The auhtors rely on data extracted from a Pakistani university. Boosted Trees outperforms bagging when dataset is larger, while stacking is better for smaller datasets. ",
      "raw": {
        "object": "block",
